short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyze and categorize search results for easier navigation, with readability score

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This InsightfulBrowse: SearchLens Chrome extension analyzes and categorizes search results on Google search pages. It adds category tags to each search result based on the content type (News, Blog, Academic, Commercial, Social Media, or Other) and performs a simple readability analysis (Easy, Medium, or Complex) on the search result snippets.
